 * 
 * ✅ Single-line comments with //
 * ✅ Multi-line comments with /* */
 * ✅ JSDoc-style documentation
 * ✅ Inline annotations
 * ✅ Section headers
 * ✅ Code documentation blocks
 * ✅ TODO/FIXME/NOTE markers
 * ✅ Commented-out code preservation
 * 
